    "description": "<strong>注意：本游戏仅限VR使用。</strong><br><br>Primitier是一款高度灵活的VR沙盒游戏，您可以在基于物理模拟的广阔世界中自由切割和连接物体来创建工具和机械。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >真实工艺系统</h2>用石头敲击树木，树木会在撞击点被切断。将石头附在合适长度的木材末端，就可以制作出石斧。通过这种方式，您可以以一种真实的工艺感制作各种工具，不仅限于木材和石头，几乎所有在游戏中找到的物品都可以使用。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745170/extras/3726f808988ba092eade6134c54e5e14.poster.avif?t=1747840270\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745170/extras/3726f808988ba092eade6134c54e5e14.webm?t=1747840270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745170/extras/3726f808988ba092eade6134c54e5e14.mp4?t=1747840270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >广阔的世界</h2>您可以无缝地穿越一个广阔的、程序生成的世界。在探索过程中，您可能会遇到敌人——所以要准备好制作武器来保卫自己。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745170/extras/977ef1692631917a5dd57d37a08b8f5e.poster.avif?t=1747840270\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745170/extras/977ef1692631917a5dd57d37a08b8f5e.webm?t=1747840270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745170/extras/977ef1692631917a5dd57d37a08b8f5e.mp4?t=1747840270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >高级物理模拟</h2>包括制作的工具在内，所有物体都通过物理模拟进行交互。例如，石斧的挥动难度和破坏力取决于手柄的长度和石头的重量。您还可以制作像手推车和飞机这样的机器，并通过物理运作。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745170/extras/17032a8c4329ad3943e008154963b814.poster.avif?t=1747840270\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745170/extras/17032a8c4329ad3943e008154963b814.webm?t=1747840270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745170/extras/17032a8c4329ad3943e008154963b814.mp4?t=1747840270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>空气阻力、升力和浮力的模拟也包括在内。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745170/extras/bba96f6b11fddc7ebe7592d92aa7dbe2.poster.avif?t=1747840270\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745170/extras/bba96f6b11fddc7ebe7592d92aa7dbe2.webm?t=1747840270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745170/extras/bba96f6b11fddc7ebe7592d92aa7dbe2.mp4?t=1747840270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >头像导入</h2>您可以通过加载VRM格式文件来更改头像（并非所有VRM文件都支持）。如果需要，头像可以隐藏。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发布和直播游戏视频</h2>我们允许在我们的指南内发布和直播游戏视频。详情请参阅官方网站的指南。<br>请注意，您可以使用游戏内摄像机在PC屏幕上输出第三人称视角的视频。",
